Huaiqing.

293
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:53,800
Learning opera is hard work.

294
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,840
The opera troupe rules state

295
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:59,960
that women cannot perform on stage.

296
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,880
If you're willing,

297
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:11,359
you can stay by my side from now on.

298
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,440
After getting separated from my brother,

299
