316
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,240
Until that person

317
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:11,080
entered my life.

318
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:21,600
Who says women are inferior to men?

319
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:27,880
I, Ruan Suiqing, promise to make you succeed.
